{"tid":1055773,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"每次打完飛機心情都低落","createTime":"2019-03-10T18:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T13:53:14.000Z","uid":155262,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"078385aaafb9b419ced9a3848dac40e413586c85","tid":1055773,"uid":155262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"係因為當打完飛機，腦入面嘅多巴胺由急速分泌到變回正常或唔夠，所以變得空虛？<br />\n定係因為打完飛機之後頓時冇哂性欲，所以對周圍嘅事冇乜興趣？<br />\n有冇學術jj解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff4b350cd5e948e12d57533f2ce86bc4506d363","tid":1055773,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T19:26:40.000Z","msg":"係，個飛機越打得耐，出嘢之後個人越會有無盡空虛嘅感覺，好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263fd31e2ccbc6259a5d5b7bc51616be27d31e66","tid":1055773,"uid":154255,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T21:50:41.000Z","msg":"一直無呢種感覺，但成日聽人講<br />\n有罪惡感同失落感<br />\n打完淨係累"},{"pid":"603b2791c0944ed33be2bda5cd4d01c9e83849d0","tid":1055773,"uid":150609,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T21:56:28.000Z","msg":"打完篤飛機之後百感交集<br />\n<br />\n好滿足 而又好空虛 快感一閃即逝 領悟到剎那光輝唔係永恆 世界因為咁樣才美麗<br />\n就好像人生一樣<br />\n每一篤飛機都有唔同既品味 同體會"},{"pid":"6fcf209bdbd3d8421a5e9d6b317423cc6d2b7064","tid":1055773,"uid":116614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"打一次飛機爽一時<br />\n打好多次飛機爽好多次<br />\n<br />\n打完心情低落咪打多次囉"},{"pid":"679de20cce1e6fa58d7764bc794cc09bc11f4614","tid":1055773,"uid":56999,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5DgBUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5DgBUM.jpg&h=025da24f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9b3735099c784acc577e8f3bf081d36a94f847c","tid":1055773,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"等我含射你 就唔低落"},{"pid":"41b7de4ae1a0241bb15056531dcda3bcdb3f3f62","tid":1055773,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"如果越打越精神，啲人打飛機打到死都似。<br />\n兩個可能，一，冇人屌閪，人類絕種。二，男人打到停唔到，虛脫死，冇晒男人，人類絕種。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbe05a3261227cba794c4eb99047617cd6c153f","tid":1055773,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"打太密"},{"pid":"5d89e087b89b5a72d8d7c85b23c65dd14eb3a945","tid":1055773,"uid":128223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4dd50a8a0d3d1b995e4c860cca8eac47876227c","tid":1055773,"uid":1655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"所以臨訓先打，或者打完就去訓，唔會諗咁多"},{"pid":"088bf9b8fdbc4efc3f8433fda5ba792b3f080c81","tid":1055773,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"醫生 : 連登仔，你怎麼了?<br />\n<br />\n連登仔: 每次打完飛機都心情低落<br />\n<br />\n醫生 : 咁你就打少d飛機啦 仆街"},{"pid":"4fec3170f28061005cc345107ea670e65c030010","tid":1055773,"uid":158270,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:23:56.000Z","msg":"射完之後會檢討自己點解射得出，對自己嘅品味感到內疚，又對自己受人性束縛，不能破解感到無奈。或者，天主教對人性嘅貶低就係源自性高潮後對人性嘅觀察。<br />\n然後，我又會諗下點解高潮前後我嘅審美觀會有咁大變化。明明係同一條女，點解會有咁大分別？就算係喺打緊飛機途中，我都諗緊佢有咩咁吸引，但我答唔出，淨係打得出。<br />\n完事之後，冷靜落嚟，我發現吸唔吸引只不過係生理判斷，至少有部分係取決我嘅狀態。去到依度，我又明白咩係色即是空，空即是色。我睇到物件A，唔係因為A係某個相貌，而係我生理上令到我睇到經我過濾、詮釋嘅A。<br />\n我熟練地清理現場，我忽然領悟到如果連我自己都嘅睇法都會成日變，何況係人與人之間嘅差別？之前聽到嘅南亞裔非禮阿婆新聞，個南亞人睇嚟真係精蟲上腦，連阿婆都搞。"},{"pid":"72093c9ee38e60bad37934bf053774197ccb8fee","tid":1055773,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"679de20cce1e6fa58d7764bc794cc09bc11f4614","tid":1055773,"uid":56999,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5DgBUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5DgBUM.jpg&h=025da24f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"Trump's face"},{"pid":"6806842844c6c7154359f5038d6289e6ad83fc2d","tid":1055773,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ifun01.com/images/2017/07/01/19/0356_VnqyjD_GXNxfW.jpg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifun01.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F19%2F0356_VnqyjD_GXNxfW.jpg%21r800x0.jpg&h=da2d5743&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52cb562897a0ffe3ab0e98fc67b814185281b1a3","tid":1055773,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6806842844c6c7154359f5038d6289e6ad83fc2d","tid":1055773,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ifun01.com/images/2017/07/01/19/0356_VnqyjD_GXNxfW.jpg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifun01.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F19%2F0356_VnqyjD_GXNxfW.jpg%21r800x0.jpg&h=da2d5743&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射完就係咁<br />\n係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n打飛機同做愛<br />\n都係射果刻興奮<br />\n我打飛機射完仲乾手淨腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2839593efa5aafb40b664a883e671586178a538a","tid":1055773,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fec3170f280